parametrizedQuery.name: VisitDurationOverTime

from WaitTimeStatsHistory v,

order by lastTime;

parametrizedQuery.name: PatientsPerProvider
parametrizedQuery.sourceText: CREATE NAMEDQUERY PatientsPerProvider select to_int((cvpa.pacount*100/(cvpr.prcount * chr.hrcount)))/100.0 as ppp from (select count(*) as pacount from (select patientId from CurrentVisitStatus where providerId is not null group by patientId) cvp) cvpa, (select count(*) as prcount from (select providerId from CurrentVisitStatus group by providerId) cpr) cvpr, (select count(*) as hrcount from (select hourOfDay from CurrentVisitStatus where providerId is not null group by hourOfDay) ch) chr
parametrizedQuery.queryDefinition:
select to_int((cvpa.pacount*100/(cvpr.prcount * chr.hrcount)))/100.0 as ppp
from (select count(*) as pacount 
	  from (select patientId 
			from CurrentVisitStatus 
			where providerId is not null 
			group by patientId) cvp) cvpa,
	(select count(*) as prcount 
	 from (select providerId 
		   from CurrentVisitStatus 
		   group by providerId) cpr) cvpr,
	(select count(*) as hrcount 
	 from (select hourOfDay 
		   from CurrentVisitStatus 
		   where providerId is not null 
		   group by hourOfDay) ch) chr;

parametrizedQuery.name: ActiveVisitsForHospital
parametrizedQuery.sourceText: CREATE NAMEDQUERY ActiveVisitsForHospital select sum(s.visits) as visits from (select stage, case when stage = "Arrived" then 1 when stage = "Waiting" then 2 when stage = "Assessment" then 3 else 4 end stageNumber, count(*) as visits from CurrentVisitStatus v where (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId) and stage <> "Discharged" and stage <> "Admitted" and stage <> "Left" group by stage) s
parametrizedQuery.queryDefinition:
select sum(s.visits) as visits
from
(select stage, 
case when stage = "Arrived" then 1 
     when stage = "Waiting" then 2 
	 when stage = "Assessment" then 3 
	 else 4 end stageNumber, 
	 count(*) as visits
from CurrentVisitStatus v 
where (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId)
and stage <> "Discharged" 
and stage <> "Admitted" 
and stage <> "Left" 
group by stage) s;

parametrizedQuery.name: GetCurrentVisitsForHospital
parametrizedQuery.sourceText: CREATE NAMEDQUERY GetCurrentVisitsForHospital select v.hospitalId as id, v.hospitalname as name, last(v.hospitallat) as lat, last(v.hospitallon) as lon, max(CASE WHEN stage = "Waiting" THEN v.visitDuration ELSE 0 END) as waitTime, CASE WHEN waitTime < 45 THEN "Normal" WHEN waitTime >=45 AND waitTime < 60 THEN "Medium" ELSE "High" END as waitStatus, count(*) as num from CurrentVisitStatus v where (:HospitalId is null or v.hospitalId = :HospitalId) and stage <> "Discharged" and stage <> "Admitted" and stage <> "Left" group by name
parametrizedQuery.queryDefinition:
select 
  v.hospitalId as id,
  v.hospitalname as name, 
  last(v.hospitallat) as lat, 
  last(v.hospitallon) as lon, 
  max(CASE WHEN stage = "Waiting" THEN v.visitDuration
	  ELSE 0 END) as waitTime,
  CASE WHEN waitTime < 45 THEN "Normal" 
       WHEN waitTime >=45 AND waitTime < 60 THEN "Medium"
	   ELSE "High" END as waitStatus,
  count(*) as num
from CurrentVisitStatus v 
where (:HospitalId is null or v.hospitalId = :HospitalId)
and stage <> "Discharged" 
and stage <> "Admitted" 
and stage <> "Left" 
group by name;

parametrizedQuery.name: RoomOccupancyForHospital
parametrizedQuery.sourceText: CREATE NAMEDQUERY RoomOccupancyForHospital select to_int((cvr.occupiedRooms*100)/r.allrooms) as occ from (select count(*) as occupiedRooms from (select roomId from CurrentVisitStatus where (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId) group by roomId) vr) cvr, (select count(*) as allrooms from Rooms where (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId)) r
parametrizedQuery.queryDefinition:
select to_int((cvr.occupiedRooms*100)/r.allrooms) as occ
from 
 (select count(*) as occupiedRooms
  from (select roomId from CurrentVisitStatus
		where (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId)
		group by roomId) vr) cvr, 
 (select count(*) as allrooms 
  from Rooms
  where (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId)) r;

parametrizedQuery.name: GetStageTimesByRoom
parametrizedQuery.sourceText: CREATE NAMEDQUERY GetStageTimesByRoom SELECT b.roomId as roomId, (CASE WHEN b.stage = "Waiting" THEN "Waiting" ELSE r.name END) as roomName, (CASE WHEN b.stage = "Waiting" THEN "Waiting" ELSE r.roomType END) as roomType, b.waitTime as waitTime, b.stage as stage FROM (SELECT v.roomId as roomId, MAX(v.stageDuration) as waitTime, v.stage as stage FROM CurrentVisitStatus v where (:HospitalId is null or v.hospitalId = :HospitalId) and (stage = "Waiting" or (stage="Assessment" and roomId is not null) or (stage="Treatment" and roomId is not null)) GROUP BY stage, roomId) b LEFT OUTER JOIN Rooms r ON r.id = b.roomId ORDER BY roomName
parametrizedQuery.queryDefinition:
SELECT 
  b.roomId as roomId,
  (CASE WHEN b.stage = "Waiting" THEN "Waiting"
   ELSE r.name END) as roomName,
   (CASE WHEN b.stage = "Waiting" THEN "Waiting"
   ELSE r.roomType END) as roomType,
  b.waitTime as waitTime,
  b.stage as stage
FROM
(SELECT v.roomId as roomId, 
 MAX(v.stageDuration) as waitTime,  
 v.stage as stage 
 FROM CurrentVisitStatus v 
 where (:HospitalId is null or v.hospitalId = :HospitalId) and 
 (stage = "Waiting" or 
  (stage="Assessment" and roomId is not null) or
  (stage="Treatment" and roomId is not null)) 
 GROUP BY stage, roomId) b
 LEFT OUTER JOIN Rooms r
 ON r.id = b.roomId
 ORDER BY roomName;

parametrizedQuery.name: PreviousVisitsByDiagnosis
parametrizedQuery.sourceText: CREATE NAMEDQUERY PreviousVisitsByDiagnosis select diagnosis, diagnosiscode, stage, TO_INT((count(*) * 10000)/c.totalCases)/100.0 as cases, cases + "%" as casesText from CurrentVisitStatus v, (select max(v2.timestamp) as maxts from CurrentVisitStatus v2) m, (select count(*) as totalCases from CurrentVisitStatus v3, (select max(v2.timestamp) as maxts from CurrentVisitStatus v2) m2 where (stage == "Discharged" or stage == "Admitted") and (:HospitalId is null or :HospitalId = hospitalId) and v3.timestamp > DSUBTRACT(m2.maxts, DDAYS(1))) c where (stage == "Discharged" or stage == "Admitted") and (:HospitalId is null or :HospitalId = hospitalId) and v.timestamp > DSUBTRACT(m.maxts, DDAYS(1)) group by diagnosis,stage order by cases desc
parametrizedQuery.queryDefinition:
select diagnosis, 
     diagnosiscode,
	 stage,
	 TO_INT((count(*) * 10000)/c.totalCases)/100.0 as cases,
	 cases + "%" as casesText
from CurrentVisitStatus v,
    (select max(v2.timestamp) as maxts from CurrentVisitStatus v2) m,
	(select count(*) as totalCases
	 from CurrentVisitStatus v3,
	 (select max(v2.timestamp) as maxts from CurrentVisitStatus v2) m2
	 where (stage == "Discharged" 
	        or stage == "Admitted")
	 and (:HospitalId is null or :HospitalId = hospitalId)
	 and v3.timestamp > DSUBTRACT(m2.maxts, DDAYS(1))) c
where (stage == "Discharged" 
or stage == "Admitted")
and (:HospitalId is null or :HospitalId = hospitalId)
and v.timestamp > DSUBTRACT(m.maxts, DDAYS(1))
group by diagnosis,stage
order by cases desc;

parametrizedQuery.name: PatientsPerProviderForHospital
parametrizedQuery.sourceText: CREATE NAMEDQUERY PatientsPerProviderForHospital select to_int((cvpa.pacount*100/(cvpr.prcount * chr.hrcount)))/100.0 as ppp from (select count(*) as pacount from (select patientId from CurrentVisitStatus where providerId is not null and (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId) group by patientId) cvp) cvpa, (select count(*) as prcount from (select providerId from CurrentVisitStatus where (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId) group by providerId) cpr) cvpr, (select count(*) as hrcount from (select hourOfDay from CurrentVisitStatus where providerId is not null and (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId) group by hourOfDay) ch) chr
parametrizedQuery.queryDefinition:
select to_int((cvpa.pacount*100/(cvpr.prcount * chr.hrcount)))/100.0 as ppp
from (select count(*) as pacount 
	  from (select patientId 
			from CurrentVisitStatus 
			where providerId is not null 
			and (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId)
			group by patientId) cvp) cvpa,
	(select count(*) as prcount 
	 from (select providerId 
		   from CurrentVisitStatus
		   where (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId)
		   group by providerId) cpr) cvpr,
	(select count(*) as hrcount 
	 from (select hourOfDay 
		   from CurrentVisitStatus 
		   where providerId is not null
		   and (:HospitalId is null or hospitalId = :HospitalId)
		   group by hourOfDay) ch) chr;

parametrizedQuery.name: VisitDurationOverTimeForHospital
parametrizedQuery.sourceText: CREATE NAMEDQUERY VisitDurationOverTimeForHospital select max(visitduration) as maxdur, avg(visitduration) as avgdur, hourOfDay, max(v.timestamp) as lastTime from CurrentVisitStatus v, (select max(v2.timestamp) as maxts from CurrentVisitStatus v2) m where v.timestamp > DSUBTRACT(m.maxts, DDAYS(2)) and (:HospitalId is null or :HospitalID = hospitalId) group by hourOfDay order by lastTime
parametrizedQuery.queryDefinition:
select max(visitduration) as maxdur,
	   avg(visitduration) as avgdur,
       hourOfDay,
	   max(v.timestamp) as lastTime
from CurrentVisitStatus v,
(select max(v2.timestamp) as maxts from CurrentVisitStatus v2) m
where v.timestamp > DSUBTRACT(m.maxts, DDAYS(2))
and (:HospitalId is null or :HospitalID = hospitalId)
group by hourOfDay
order by lastTime;

parametrizedQuery.queryDefinition:
